    <h3>Our History</h3>
    <p>Midpoint National was founded in 1988 as an order fulfillment services provider. From the outset we built the business by creating customized IT systems and technology to meet unique client needs. This is a strength that allows us to attract major companies and organizations and provide them with innovative, flexible solutions.

The management staff at Midpoint National has extensive general management and consulting - as well as warehousing and distribution - experience. This industry knowledge is a key reason why Midpoint National's solutions are innovative and focused on the unique needs of each client..</p>

  <h3>Our Distribution Center</h3>
   <p>   Our main objective is to ensure speed and accuracy in processing orders.</p>
   <p>The Midpoint National order distribution center is a modern reinforced concrete building planned specifically for fast, efficient distribution:</p>
     


<ul>
    <li>Over 70,000 square feet of storage, order processing, call center and administrative space</li>
    <li>11 dock doors, 22-foot ceiling heights, automatic conveyors and 3,500 flow-rail picking locations</li>
    <li>Remotely-monitored fire and burglary protection throughout</li>
    <li>Backup inventory kept in an equally well-equipped supplementary warehouse containing 100,000 additional square feet</li>
   
</ul>




   
